---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About | James Young">
  <Fragment slot="sidebar">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-terminal-dim text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Navigation</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-1">
          <li>
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 py-1.5 px-2 rounded text-sm text-terminal-dim hover:bg-terminal-accent/10 hover:text-terminal-accent transition-colors">
              <span class="text-terminal-accent/50">←</span>
              <span>Back to Home</span>
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Fragment>

  <div class="max-w-2xl">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <span class="text-terminal-accent font-mono text-sm">~/about</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-terminal-text mt-4 mb-6">
        About Me
      </h1>
    </header>

    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-terminal">
      <p class="text-terminal-text text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        I'm a machine learning and AI expert focused on turning complex ML capabilities 
        into tangible business outcomes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-terminal-text mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-terminal-accent">▸</span> What I Do
      </h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4 text-terminal-dim">
        <p>
          I specialize in the intersection of advanced ML techniques and real-world 
          applications. This means taking methods like causal inference, interpretable 
          ML, and large language models—and deploying them in ways that actually move 
          business metrics.
        </p>
        <p>
          My work spans revenue optimization, operational automation, and strategic 
          expansion analysis. I've helped companies reduce costs, increase conversion 
          rates, and make better decisions with data.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-terminal-text mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-terminal-accent">▸</span> My Approach
      </h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4 text-terminal-dim">
        <p>
          I believe in ML that you can explain. Black-box models have their place, 
          but the most valuable insights come when you can tell stakeholders not just 
          <em>what</em> to do, but <em>why</em>.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm also obsessive about MLOps—because a model that can't be deployed, 
          monitored, and maintained isn't really a solution.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-terminal-text mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-terminal-accent">▸</span> Get in Touch
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-terminal-dim mb-6">
        I'm always interested in discussing interesting ML problems. Reach out on 
        LinkedIn or subscribe to my newsletter for regular insights.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jamesyoungsd/" 
           target="_blank"
           rel="noopener noreferrer"
           class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-terminal-accent text-terminal-bg font-medium text-sm rounded hover:shadow-glow transition-shadow">
          LinkedIn →
        </a>
        <a href="/newsletter" 
           class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 border border-terminal-accent text-terminal-accent font-medium text-sm rounded hover:bg-terminal-accent/10 transition-colors">
          Newsletter
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</Base>
